00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.840
 In Sarnath, he gives the teaching, so tomorrow is that day, the Buddha gives the process teaching.

00:00:05.840 --> 00:00:12.600
 Teaching is concentrating on his enlightenment, or the result of his enlightenment.

00:00:12.600 --> 00:00:19.480
 When you get enlightened, you become Buddha, and then his realisation, his knowledge and experience

00:00:19.480 --> 00:00:21.200
 begin to share to the others.

00:00:21.200 --> 00:00:27.560
 That is really teaching, so it is, as we all know, teaching is allowed, kind in the completion,

00:00:27.560 --> 00:00:32.840
 how to make ourselves stronger and make beneficial to ourselves, all of that.

00:00:32.840 --> 00:00:38.880
 So that is really, tomorrow, according to very basic, and that is considered a very special day.

00:00:38.880 --> 00:00:45.640
 So that's it, and so according to a kind of normal schedule level, I think Buddha is just

00:00:45.640 --> 00:00:47.880
 approaching Varanasi tonight.

00:00:47.880 --> 00:00:50.880
 [Laughter]

00:00:50.880 --> 00:00:53.640
 And tomorrow he is going to walk in Sarnath.

00:00:53.640 --> 00:00:59.960
