00:01:04.620 --> 00:01:05.040
 that."

00:01:05.040 --> 00:01:10.400
 But Buddha came foremost to see them, and also could give the teaching at Sarnath.

00:01:10.400 --> 00:01:18.880
 So all that big history, things are happening today and tomorrow, so tomorrow is actually the day

00:01:18.880 --> 00:01:20.240
 that we are going to be looking at.

